flowRoot.flowPara: <sc>Once</sc> <sc>upon a time,</sc> <sc>there was a girl with</sc> <sc>long golden hair</sc>. <sc>Of course, she was not con-tent to remain in her tower, and yearned with all her heart to feel the grass below.</sc>
<sc>Once upon a time, there was a girl with long golden hair. Of course, she was not con-tent to remain in her tower, and yearned with all her heart to feel the grass below.</sc>
